each Player, you do not indicate whether it was a vote or a
declaration of Presence you received from that Player, and that you
list all the Players who have voted or declared Presence, regardless
of when they voted.  Nothing prevents you, in my opinion, from
splitting the list into those who voted before, and those who voted
after, P3533 took effect.

