Again, I think it's better to have catch-all phrasing in these to keep the
Indulgence balance even at all times. As for this system, as mentioned in
my other e-mail, I may suggest that we just go to a "self-directed PO"
system for this, as it'll standardize the whole thing and make this Rule so
much simpler -- if there are too many Blots, the Bank makes Indulgences, if
there are too many Indulgences, the Bank gets issued Blots. 


